title: CrazyCars3D
description:
CrazyCars3d - it is arcadian platformer on machines, you should stop the destroying hurricane to save residuals of the destroyed world. The project is developed on an engine Unity5 and we create all content, including writing of a code, music.
Prehistory - Cars lived and flourished on their planet, but misfortune - alien beings have sown evil and chaos in their world, destroying the planet in order to usurp valuable resources. You will manage one of the surviving machines of this world, to destroy the enemy ancient weapon, which will be found in this ruined world
